name: Race Parking Car 3D
description:
Race Parking Car 3D is an amazing car parking simulator game that requires highest precision! The parking situation in game will require you to show top skills in steering, acceleration, and obstacle avoidance to get those vehicles parked in parking places.
FEATURES
- PARKING SENSOR
- REAL CAR SOUND
- IN CAMERA VIEW
- DETAILED INTERIORS
- REALISTIC GRAPHIC QUALITY
